<font color="yellow">It's breaking my heart.</font>

418
00:28:19,619 --> 00:28:20,719
<font color="yellow">Honey.</font>

419
00:28:23,519 --> 00:28:25,179
<font color="yellow">How did I...</font>

420
00:28:29,049 --> 00:28:30,049
<font color="yellow">Father.</font>

421
00:28:30,219 --> 00:28:31,279
<font color="yellow">Hye Joo.</font>

422
00:28:31,449 --> 00:28:32,979
<font color="yellow">The doctor finished his examination.</font>

423
00:28:33,819 --> 00:28:35,049
<font color="yellow">They moved him into a room.</font>

424
00:28:47,279 --> 00:28:48,349
<font color="yellow">Seong Hoon.</font>

425
00:28:52,379 --> 00:28:53,449
<font color="yellow">Seong Hoon.</font>

426
00:28:54,519 --> 00:28:56,119
<font color="yellow">How are you feeling?</font>

427
00:28:56,979 --> 00:28:57,979
<font color="yellow">Mother.</font>

428
00:28:59,049 --> 00:29:00,279
<font color="yellow">Yes, Seong Hoon.</font>

429
00:29:01,679 --> 00:29:04,419
<font color="yellow">Look at you. What's all this?</font>

430
00:29:05,019 --> 00:29:07,379
<font color="yellow">I really have no idea what's with you.</font>

431
00:29:07,879 --> 00:29:09,079
<font color="yellow">I am sorry.</font>

432
00:29:09,679 --> 00:29:13,079
<font color="yellow">We have to wait for the examination results,</font>

433
00:29:13,849 --> 00:29:16,879
<font color="yellow">but the doctor said his spine and brain seem to be okay.</font>

434
00:29:17,449 --> 00:29:18,679
<font color="yellow">- Really? - Yes.</font>

435
00:29:18,779 --> 00:29:19,779
<font color="yellow">Thank goodness.</font>

436
00:29:20,379 --> 00:29:23,249
<font color="yellow">I'm relieved to hear that.</font>

437
00:29:29,819 --> 00:29:30,819
<font color="yellow">You're back.</font>

438
00:29:31,249 --> 00:29:34,419
<font color="yellow">What happened to him? Why didn't you call me?</font>

439
00:29:34,879 --> 00:29:36,149
<font color="yellow">Mother,</font>

440
00:29:36,579 --> 00:29:38,819
<font color="yellow">I had no time to make a phone call.</font>

441
00:29:38,819 --> 00:29:40,119
<font color="yellow">So is Seong Hoon okay?</font>

442
00:29:41,019 --> 00:29:42,149
<font color="yellow">He is.</font>

443
00:29:42,519 --> 00:29:46,119
<font color="yellow">He fractured his leg and arm. Other than that, he's fine.</font>

444
00:29:48,149 --> 00:29:49,749
<font color="yellow">Thank goodness he's safe.</font>

445
00:29:50,449 --> 00:29:52,879
<font color="yellow">Still, he has to stay in the hospital for a few days,</font>

446
00:29:53,119 --> 00:29:55,919
<font color="yellow">so Hye Joo is packing downstairs.</font>

447
00:29:55,919 --> 00:29:57,419
<font color="yellow">Then, who's at the hospital now?</font>

448
00:29:58,019 --> 00:29:59,279
<font color="yellow">Hyung Seop is.</font>

449
00:30:00,579 --> 00:30:01,579
<font color="yellow">Mother,</font>

450
00:30:02,279 --> 00:30:04,219
<font color="yellow">can I go downstairs and take some rest?</font>

451
00:30:04,219 --> 00:30:06,449
<font color="yellow">Of course. Go have some rest.</font>

452
00:30:06,719 --> 00:30:09,449
<font color="yellow">Ms. Oh, please don't worry too much.</font>

453
00:30:09,979 --> 00:30:11,549
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

454
00:30:11,879 --> 00:30:14,249
<font color="yellow">Please put yourself together and sleep tight.</font>

455
00:30:14,249 --> 00:30:17,849
<font color="yellow">I'm worried that you might also fall ill.</font>

456
00:30:21,219 --> 00:30:22,379
<font color="yellow">Goodness.</font>

457
00:30:56,379 --> 00:30:58,879
<font color="yellow">I have to sleep over at the hospital.</font>

458
00:30:59,319 --> 00:31:01,349
<font color="yellow">Please take care of Ah In, okay?</font>

459
00:31:02,019 --> 00:31:04,449
<font color="yellow">- Is it really bad? - No, he's okay.</font>

460
00:31:04,719 --> 00:31:06,449
<font color="yellow">He just needs to stay there for a few days.</font>

461
00:31:06,549 --> 00:31:10,779
<font color="yellow">Mom, I miss Dad.</font>

462
00:31:10,919 --> 00:31:13,549
<font color="yellow">Come here, my Ah In.</font>

463
00:31:13,779 --> 00:31:16,349
<font color="yellow">You're such a good girl. He's all right.</font>

464
00:31:16,849 --> 00:31:19,279
<font color="yellow">Stop crying. Don't worry.</font>

465
00:31:25,079 --> 00:31:27,249
<font color="yellow">I need you to make kids dinner.</font>

466
00:31:27,979 --> 00:31:30,979
<font color="yellow">- Why do I have to? - Let's talk about...</font>

467
00:31:31,379 --> 00:31:33,879
<font color="yellow">our old grudges and our switched kids later.</font>

468
00:31:38,249 --> 00:31:40,749
<font color="yellow">Seong Hoon had an accident,</font>

469
00:31:40,749 --> 00:31:42,549
<font color="yellow">so I have to stay at the hospital.</font>

470
00:31:43,179 --> 00:31:45,249
<font color="yellow">Gosh, what happened to him?</font>

471
00:31:45,319 --> 00:31:46,679
<font color="yellow">I'll explain later.</font>

472
00:31:47,679 --> 00:31:51,579
<font color="yellow">Make dinner for Chang Soo, Ah In, and Ji Hoon, okay?</font>

473
00:31:53,719 --> 00:31:55,579
<font color="yellow">Hye Joo!</font>

474
00:31:58,619 --> 00:31:59,619
<font color="yellow">Mom.</font>

475
00:32:00,579 --> 00:32:02,919
<font color="yellow">I mean, Aunt.</font>

476
00:32:03,619 --> 00:32:06,379
<font color="yellow">I can't believe you are so peaceful right now.</font>

477
00:32:06,449 --> 00:32:09,679
<font color="yellow">Your ex-father is in the hospital.</font>

478
00:32:09,849 --> 00:32:11,519
<font color="yellow">How could you possibly enjoy that hot dog?</font>

479
00:32:11,649 --> 00:32:13,079
<font color="yellow">Is he in a hospital now?</font>

480
00:32:13,519 --> 00:32:17,449
<font color="yellow">I need you to take good care of Ji Hoon and Ah In, okay?</font>

481
00:32:19,249 --> 00:32:21,149
<font color="yellow">Mom.</font>

482
00:32:28,419 --> 00:32:30,179
<font color="yellow">- Where's Ji Hoon? - He said he doesn't want to eat.</font>

483
00:32:31,779 --> 00:32:32,879
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

484
00:32:33,049 --> 00:32:34,619
<font color="yellow">("This time, I'm a magician")</font>

485
00:32:36,649 --> 00:32:37,779
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon.</font>

486
00:32:40,379 --> 00:32:43,279
<font color="yellow">- Yes? - Why are you not having dinner?</font>

487
00:32:44,449 --> 00:32:45,719
<font color="yellow">I'm not hungry.</font>

488
00:32:50,649 --> 00:32:52,419
<font color="yellow">Isn't it because you don't want to see me?</font>

489
00:32:57,819 --> 00:33:00,019
<font color="yellow">What book were you reading just now?</font>

490
00:33:00,879 --> 00:33:03,049
<font color="yellow">- It's nothing. - Give it to me.</font>

491
00:33:03,979 --> 00:33:07,119
<font color="yellow">- I don't want to. - Do you know what time it is?</font>

492
00:33:07,849 --> 00:33:10,319
<font color="yellow">You must be receiving your private lesson at this hour.</font>

493
00:33:10,379 --> 00:33:12,079
<font color="yellow">Why are you reading a useless book like that?</font>

494
00:33:12,679 --> 00:33:14,549
<font color="yellow">- Give it to me already. - I don't want to.</font>

495
00:33:15,979 --> 00:33:17,749
<font color="yellow">Is that why you wanted to live here?</font>

496
00:33:17,819 --> 00:33:20,649
<font color="yellow">You decided to live here so that you can waste as much time as you want?</font>

497
00:33:21,519 --> 00:33:23,379
<font color="yellow">Did you abandon your mom...</font>

498
00:33:23,919 --> 00:33:25,849
<font color="yellow">who raised you for 15 years for this?</font>

499
00:33:26,149 --> 00:33:27,519
<font color="yellow">Give the book to me!</font>

500
00:33:28,179 --> 00:33:31,019
<font color="yellow">I said no! You're not even my mom.</font>

501
00:33:31,449 --> 00:33:33,349
<font color="yellow">Why do you care about me?</font>

502
00:33:38,719 --> 00:33:40,249
<font color="yellow">What? Ji Hoon!</font>

503
00:33:43,649 --> 00:33:46,649
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon, stop right there! Ji Hoon!</font>

504
00:33:50,549 --> 00:33:51,649
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon!</font>

505
00:33:52,449 --> 00:33:54,349
<font color="yellow">How can you do this to me?</font>

506
00:33:54,649 --> 00:33:56,619
<font color="yellow">I put all my time and efforts for you.</font>

507
00:33:56,979 --> 00:33:58,719
<font color="yellow">I devoted all my life to you!</font>

508
00:33:59,319 --> 00:34:02,789
<font color="yellow">How can you change your attitude toward me this quickly?</font>

509
00:34:03,419 --> 00:34:04,879
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon!</font>

510
00:34:07,919 --> 00:34:09,579
<font color="yellow">Ah In, stop crying.</font>

511
00:34:09,749 --> 00:34:11,049
<font color="yellow">Don't cry.</font>

512
00:34:11,649 --> 00:34:14,819
<font color="yellow">It's all right. Stop crying.</font>

513
00:34:18,549 --> 00:34:19,579
<font color="yellow">Grandma.</font>

514
00:34:20,679 --> 00:34:22,819
<font color="yellow">Gosh, you're here.</font>

515
00:34:24,249 --> 00:34:25,419
<font color="yellow">Here is my Ah In.</font>

516
00:34:25,819 --> 00:34:27,319
<font color="yellow">Grandma.</font>

517
00:34:27,749 --> 00:34:30,289
<font color="yellow">It's good to see you. My little girl.</font>

518
00:34:30,519 --> 00:34:33,349
<font color="yellow">Ah In kept crying because Mom and Dad are away.</font>

519
00:34:34,979 --> 00:34:36,449
<font color="yellow">- Grandma. - It's okay.</font>

520
00:34:37,179 --> 00:34:40,019
<font color="yellow">This is my cute Ah In.</font>

521
00:34:40,119 --> 00:34:42,579
<font color="yellow">My poor kids.</font>

522
00:34:47,619 --> 00:34:50,319
<font color="yellow">Dad, please go home.</font>

523
00:34:51,379 --> 00:34:53,379
<font color="yellow">Hye Joo will be here soon.</font>

524
00:34:54,579 --> 00:34:55,749
<font color="yellow">Please go home.</font>

525
00:34:59,919 --> 00:35:01,319
<font color="yellow">Did you drink?</font>

526
00:35:04,079 --> 00:35:05,789
<font color="yellow">Is that really true?</font>

527
00:35:08,349 --> 00:35:10,679
<font color="yellow">- Yes. - Why did you do that?</font>

528
00:35:11,819 --> 00:35:14,149
<font color="yellow">Well, I just had a little...</font>

529
00:35:17,579 --> 00:35:21,379
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you tell me earlier if things were that tough?</font>

530
00:35:22,319 --> 00:35:25,179
<font color="yellow">I cannot ask for your help any more. It's too shameless.</font>

531
00:35:27,789 --> 00:35:30,079
<font color="yellow">Still, I'm your father.</font>

532
00:35:31,219 --> 00:35:32,249
<font color="yellow">Father.</font>

533
00:35:33,419 --> 00:35:35,749
<font color="yellow">There's no need to feel shameless to your parents.</font>

534
00:35:36,849 --> 00:35:38,519
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry to trouble you so often.</font>

535
00:35:39,579 --> 00:35:40,949
<font color="yellow">I can't say anything, but I'm sorry.</font>

536
00:35:46,319 --> 00:35:47,549
<font color="yellow">You know what?</font>

537
00:35:50,849 --> 00:35:52,579
<font color="yellow">I think you're the worst one.</font>

538
00:35:58,349 --> 00:35:59,549
<font color="yellow">Father.</font>

539
00:36:10,619 --> 00:36:11,679
<font color="yellow">Aunt.</font>

540
00:36:12,449 --> 00:36:13,519
<font color="yellow">Chang Soo.</font>

541
00:36:14,419 --> 00:36:16,179
<font color="yellow">- Grandma. - You're back.</font>

542
00:36:16,519 --> 00:36:20,289
<font color="yellow">Seong Hoon had an accident, so the kids came up here.</font>

543
00:36:20,549 --> 00:36:21,579
<font color="yellow">Sorry?</font>

544
00:36:22,419 --> 00:36:25,419
<font color="yellow">It's all right.</font>

545
00:36:25,549 --> 00:36:28,119
<font color="yellow">My little Ah In is a good girl.</font>

546
00:36:28,879 --> 00:36:29,879
<font color="yellow">It's okay.</font>

547
00:36:31,079 --> 00:36:32,179
<font color="yellow">So...</font>

548
00:36:33,149 --> 00:36:36,149
<font color="yellow">I want you to go downstairs and take care of Seong Hoon's kids.</font>

549
00:36:36,449 --> 00:36:39,419
<font color="yellow">They must be in a daze now.</font>

550
00:36:41,419 --> 00:36:42,649
<font color="yellow">I will. Don't worry.</font>

551
00:36:43,819 --> 00:36:45,579
<font color="yellow">I'll stay over at the hospital, then.</font>

552
00:36:47,379 --> 00:36:50,649
<font color="yellow">Hye Joo and your dad are staying there.</font>

553
00:36:51,119 --> 00:36:53,249
<font color="yellow">There's no room for you.</font>

554
00:36:53,349 --> 00:36:55,379
<font color="yellow">Please just take care of the kids.</font>

555
00:36:56,849 --> 00:36:57,979
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

556
00:37:01,919 --> 00:37:03,749
<font color="yellow">Aunt, I can hold her.</font>

557
00:37:04,289 --> 00:37:07,179
<font color="yellow">It's all right. She wants to stay on my back.</font>

558
00:37:10,379 --> 00:37:11,449
<font color="yellow">Uncle, you're here.</font>

559
00:37:16,149 --> 00:37:18,019
<font color="yellow">Are you okay, Chang Soo?</font>

560
00:37:18,349 --> 00:37:20,679
<font color="yellow">I have no idea why things are going crazy.</font>

561
00:37:21,249 --> 00:37:23,519
<font color="yellow">We have one problem after another.</font>

562
00:37:24,249 --> 00:37:26,219
<font color="yellow">Goodness, you talk like a grownup.</font>

563
00:37:26,419 --> 00:37:28,179
<font color="yellow">- By the way, - Yes?</font>

564
00:37:28,649 --> 00:37:29,849
<font color="yellow">I need to go to bathroom.</font>

565
00:37:39,019 --> 00:37:41,449
<font color="yellow">Please let me hold Ah In. I will put her to sleep.</font>

566
00:37:41,789 --> 00:37:45,019
<font color="yellow">It's okay. She wants to be with me.</font>

567
00:37:46,819 --> 00:37:49,319
<font color="yellow">Ah In, let me hold you.</font>

568
00:37:50,249 --> 00:37:52,789
<font color="yellow">Uncle.</font>

569
00:37:52,789 --> 00:37:53,849
<font color="yellow">Come here.</font>

570
00:37:55,519 --> 00:37:56,749
<font color="yellow">Ah In.</font>

571
00:38:01,079 --> 00:38:03,289
<font color="yellow">Stay with me.</font>

572
00:38:03,819 --> 00:38:05,379
<font color="yellow">Okay. I will.</font>

573
00:38:39,019 --> 00:38:40,079
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui.</font>

574
00:38:45,289 --> 00:38:46,289
<font color="yellow">How have you been?</font>

575
00:38:48,019 --> 00:38:49,019
<font color="yellow">Good.</font>

576
00:38:49,949 --> 00:38:50,979
<font color="yellow">I just wondered...</font>

577
00:38:51,579 --> 00:38:53,349
<font color="yellow">if you've been doing well.</font>

578
00:38:55,219 --> 00:38:56,379
<font color="yellow">I'm good thanks to you.</font>

579
00:38:58,179 --> 00:38:59,219
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

580
00:39:04,549 --> 00:39:05,819
<font color="yellow">Don't worry about Ah In.</font>

581
00:39:06,379 --> 00:39:08,049
<font color="yellow">I will go down often.</font>

582
00:39:10,019 --> 00:39:11,049
<font color="yellow">Good night.</font>

583
00:39:12,549 --> 00:39:13,949
<font color="yellow">Okay, then.</font>

584
00:40:01,379 --> 00:40:03,449
<font color="yellow">("Theoretical Love")</font>

585
00:40:37,219 --> 00:40:39,319
<font color="yellow">Children are children.</font>

586
00:40:40,449 --> 00:40:42,449
<font color="yellow">Children don't think about their parents.</font>

587
00:40:44,379 --> 00:40:45,619
<font color="yellow">Get out.</font>

588
00:40:45,979 --> 00:40:47,649
<font color="yellow">Go to your room.</font>

589
00:40:48,949 --> 00:40:51,819
<font color="yellow">How can I go to my room when you are crying like this?</font>

590
00:40:53,249 --> 00:40:54,249
<font color="yellow">You...</font>

591
00:40:55,519 --> 00:40:57,289
<font color="yellow">I told you not to call me mom...</font>

592
00:40:57,749 --> 00:41:00,219
<font color="yellow">because I'm not used to the fact that you are my son.</font>

593
00:41:02,449 --> 00:41:05,049
<font color="yellow">Okay, then. I will call you Aunt.</font>

594
00:41:05,979 --> 00:41:08,019
<font color="yellow">It doesn't matter to me.</font>

595
00:41:09,179 --> 00:41:11,719
<font color="yellow">Hold on. There's an eyelash.</font>

596
00:41:11,719 --> 00:41:12,979
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

597
00:41:13,219 --> 00:41:14,649
<font color="yellow">Get that hand off me.</font>

598
00:41:24,679 --> 00:41:26,079
<font color="yellow">Why don't you go...</font>

599
00:41:26,349 --> 00:41:28,449
<font color="yellow">and find my Ji Hoon?</font>

600
00:41:28,789 --> 00:41:30,219
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon isn't home, right?</font>

601
00:41:30,449 --> 00:41:32,649
<font color="yellow">Go and look for Ji Hoon.</font>

602
00:41:41,319 --> 00:41:42,849
<font color="yellow">What a horrible child.</font>

603
00:41:43,579 --> 00:41:45,349
<font color="yellow">How can he torture you like this?</font>

604
00:41:46,679 --> 00:41:47,919
<font color="yellow">Should I hit him?</font>

605
00:41:49,119 --> 00:41:50,149
<font color="yellow">Be quiet.</font>

606
00:41:51,949 --> 00:41:53,449
<font color="yellow">Get me some more tissue.</font>

607
00:41:54,949 --> 00:41:55,949
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

608
00:42:10,149 --> 00:42:11,379
<font color="yellow">How is he?</font>

609
00:42:13,319 --> 00:42:15,249
<font color="yellow">He's with Hye Joo.</font>

610
00:42:17,979 --> 00:42:19,179
<font color="yellow">Is he in serious pain?</font>

611
00:42:19,649 --> 00:42:22,049
<font color="yellow">The nurse gave him painkiller.</font>

612
00:42:22,579 --> 00:42:25,419
<font color="yellow">How can he not feel pain? He fell off from the third floor.</font>

613
00:43:08,419 --> 00:43:09,449
<font color="yellow">President.</font>

614
00:43:10,619 --> 00:43:11,789
<font color="yellow">I'm here.</font>

615
00:43:23,579 --> 00:43:24,719
<font color="yellow">Cancel it.</font>

616
00:43:27,049 --> 00:43:28,519
<font color="yellow">Just like you told me,</font>

617
00:43:29,579 --> 00:43:31,579
<font color="yellow">cancel the pension and give it to Seong Hoon.</font>

618
00:43:32,819 --> 00:43:33,979
<font color="yellow">Honey.</font>

619
00:43:34,449 --> 00:43:36,349
<font color="yellow">My son is about to die.</font>

620
00:43:38,119 --> 00:43:41,279
<font color="yellow">What difference does money make?</font>

621
00:43:41,579 --> 00:43:42,919
<font color="yellow">Cancel it and give this to him.</font>

622
00:43:46,249 --> 00:43:48,449
<font color="yellow">I was worried that he would live longer than me.</font>

623
00:43:49,849 --> 00:43:51,779
<font color="yellow">That's why I was holding on to that money.</font>

624
00:43:52,779 --> 00:43:54,949
<font color="yellow">It wasn't just for me.</font>

625
00:43:55,679 --> 00:43:58,119
<font color="yellow">My son is about to die before me.</font>

626
00:43:59,719 --> 00:44:01,079
<font color="yellow">What different does it make?</font>

627
00:44:01,619 --> 00:44:02,649
<font color="yellow">Honey.</font>

628
00:44:02,819 --> 00:44:05,649
<font color="yellow">Cancel it tomorrow and give it to him.</font>

629
00:44:08,349 --> 00:44:11,549
