00:56:53,979 --> 00:56:56,019
<font color="yellow">They have some tea. Do you want it?</font>

840
00:56:56,019 --> 00:56:57,849
<font color="yellow">No thanks. This is enough for me.</font>

841
00:56:58,149 --> 00:56:59,249
<font color="yellow">Please sit down.</font>

842
00:56:59,549 --> 00:57:01,749
<font color="yellow">I believe all of you are...</font>

843
00:57:01,749 --> 00:57:04,779
<font color="yellow">looking for a reliable business partner...</font>

844
00:57:04,979 --> 00:57:08,249
<font color="yellow">with a profound knowledge and competitive edges.</font>

845
00:57:08,579 --> 00:57:09,579
<font color="yellow">(Mustard Chicken)</font>

846
00:57:09,579 --> 00:57:11,519
<font color="yellow">(Sweet Chicken)</font>

847
00:57:11,519 --> 00:57:12,579
<font color="yellow">(Boneless Chicken)</font>

848
00:57:17,619 --> 00:57:18,749
<font color="yellow">Have a bite.</font>

849
00:57:23,619 --> 00:57:25,419
<font color="yellow">Have you run a business before?</font>

850
00:57:25,919 --> 00:57:27,219
<font color="yellow">Penguin...</font>

851
00:57:31,119 --> 00:57:32,579
<font color="yellow">I had a large business once.</font>

852
00:57:34,949 --> 00:57:37,379
<font color="yellow">This will be his second avian business.</font>

853
00:57:40,719 --> 00:57:42,779
<font color="yellow">(I love you Dad. Please get well soon.)</font>

854
00:57:49,249 --> 00:57:52,619
<font color="yellow">- Are you having fun, Ah In? - Yes, I'm having fun.</font>

855
00:57:56,879 --> 00:57:59,149
<font color="yellow">Please get well soon, Dad.</font>

856
00:57:59,219 --> 00:58:01,649
<font color="yellow">This is my little girl.</font>

857
00:58:03,449 --> 00:58:04,719
<font color="yellow">I will.</font>

858
00:58:09,819 --> 00:58:11,279
<font color="yellow">Is there anything else?</font>

859
00:58:12,049 --> 00:58:13,119
<font color="yellow">No, that's all.</font>

860
00:58:14,149 --> 00:58:16,779
<font color="yellow">I heard that beef bone soup is good for fractures.</font>

861
00:58:18,319 --> 00:58:21,019
<font color="yellow">I already ordered bones from the butcher's shop.</font>

862
00:58:21,279 --> 00:58:22,579
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

863
00:58:26,179 --> 00:58:27,279
<font color="yellow">I'll open the door.</font>

864
00:58:30,149 --> 00:58:31,279
<font color="yellow">Hello, Sir.</font>

865
00:58:38,819 --> 00:58:40,719
<font color="yellow">It's going to take forever.</font>

866
00:58:42,279 --> 00:58:44,449
<font color="yellow">This is driving me crazy. Dong Hui.</font>

867
00:58:44,919 --> 00:58:48,019
<font color="yellow">- Yes? - Can you revise these for me?</font>

868
00:58:53,749 --> 00:58:54,779
<font color="yellow">Can I?</font>

869
00:58:54,819 --> 00:58:56,849
<font color="yellow">The writer got fed up with revising, so she just left it to us.</font>

870
00:58:56,849 --> 00:58:59,119
<font color="yellow">She's gone off the grid now.</font>

871
00:58:59,519 --> 00:59:03,449
<font color="yellow">We have to fix it and come up with a complete script.</font>

872
00:59:04,149 --> 00:59:06,179
<font color="yellow">I think you can manage this.</font>

873
00:59:07,449 --> 00:59:08,549
<font color="yellow">But can I...</font>

874
00:59:08,549 --> 00:59:09,749
<font color="yellow">Can you do it or not?</font>

875
00:59:11,049 --> 00:59:13,019
<font color="yellow">I will give it a try, then.</font>

876
00:59:13,019 --> 00:59:14,249
<font color="yellow">Okay. Please do a good job.</font>

877
00:59:16,449 --> 00:59:17,649
<font color="yellow">You're here.</font>

878
00:59:22,719 --> 00:59:24,019
<font color="yellow">You're working late.</font>

879
00:59:24,319 --> 00:59:26,619
<font color="yellow">Yes, we're not done with the work yet.</font>

880
00:59:27,949 --> 00:59:30,379
<font color="yellow">Where did Director Han go? His phone is turned off.</font>

881
00:59:30,579 --> 00:59:33,449
<font color="yellow">He left for a meeting with a TV station director.</font>

882
00:59:33,819 --> 00:59:35,579
<font color="yellow">That's why he might be out of reach.</font>

883
00:59:36,079 --> 00:59:39,149
<font color="yellow">I see. Then please tell him to come to my office when he returns.</font>

884
00:59:39,149 --> 00:59:40,379
<font color="yellow">Okay, I will do that.</font>

885
00:59:43,849 --> 00:59:45,779
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui, can I see you?</font>

886
00:59:47,579 --> 00:59:48,579
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

887
00:59:49,219 --> 00:59:50,679
<font color="yellow">So what did you decide?</font>

888
00:59:52,749 --> 00:59:53,779
<font color="yellow">Decide what?</font>

889
00:59:53,919 --> 00:59:56,219
<font color="yellow">Last time you came here and we agreed that you will...</font>

890
00:59:56,219 --> 00:59:59,179
<font color="yellow">think about what you should do for Director Han.</font>

891
01:00:00,049 --> 01:00:01,549
<font color="yellow">So what did you decide to do?</font>

892
01:00:04,819 --> 01:00:08,049
<font color="yellow">Mr. Park was praising that you work very well.</font>

893
01:00:09,119 --> 01:00:11,379
<font color="yellow">I think you decided to stay here...</font>

894
01:00:11,679 --> 01:00:14,079
<font color="yellow">and work hard.</font>

895
01:00:17,449 --> 01:00:19,779
<font color="yellow">You should talk to me. What's wrong with you?</font>

896
01:00:21,349 --> 01:00:22,419
<font color="yellow">Director.</font>

897
01:00:22,779 --> 01:00:23,949
<font color="yellow">Yes, Dong Hui.</font>

898
01:00:24,449 --> 01:00:25,519
<font color="yellow">I...</font>

899
01:00:26,979 --> 01:00:29,349
<font color="yellow">I want to keep working for this company.</font>

900
01:00:29,349 --> 01:00:30,719
<font color="yellow">I will try my best.</font>

901
01:00:30,979 --> 01:00:32,819
<font color="yellow">You don't think about Director Han, do you?</font>

902
01:00:33,719 --> 01:00:36,449
<font color="yellow">Wouldn't it be uncomfortable for you?</font>

903
01:00:37,279 --> 01:00:38,549
<font color="yellow">Since I already started working here,</font>

904
01:00:38,919 --> 01:00:42,149
<font color="yellow">I want to work hard so that I can pay for my brother's debt...</font>

905
01:00:42,449 --> 01:00:44,819
<font color="yellow">and stop being nuisance to Director Han.</font>

906
01:00:45,949 --> 01:00:47,579
<font color="yellow">I am a little smart.</font>

907
01:00:47,949 --> 01:00:51,019
<font color="yellow">That sounds like you've chosen to ignore Director Han...</font>

908
01:00:51,019 --> 01:00:52,719
<font color="yellow">and to benefit yourself.</font>

909
01:00:53,119 --> 01:00:54,519
<font color="yellow">Can I consider it like that?</font>

910
01:00:56,779 --> 01:00:58,649
<font color="yellow">Can I understand it like that?</font>

911
01:01:00,819 --> 01:01:03,879
<font color="yellow">Yes. I want to work.</font>

912
01:01:04,349 --> 01:01:05,649
<font color="yellow">Okay, then.</font>

913
01:01:06,149 --> 01:01:09,179
<font color="yellow">A high school graduate like yourself...</font>

914
01:01:09,449 --> 01:01:11,649
<font color="yellow">working for our firm is as impossible as...</font>

915
01:01:11,649 --> 01:01:13,219
<font color="yellow">a camel passing through the eye of a needle.</font>

916
01:01:13,379 --> 01:01:15,179
<font color="yellow">You can't abandon that chance...</font>

917
01:01:15,519 --> 01:01:18,779
<font color="yellow">for royalty or sense of honor to your in-law.</font>

918
01:01:19,819 --> 01:01:22,619
<font color="yellow">It's not like you've known each other for a long time...</font>

919
01:01:22,619 --> 01:01:24,649
<font color="yellow">that you would be willing to take sacrifices for him.</font>

920
01:01:25,679 --> 01:01:28,119
<font color="yellow">After you got off at the apartment in Cheonho-dong,</font>

921
01:01:28,149 --> 01:01:30,119
<font color="yellow">I had an argument with Director Han.</font>

922
01:01:31,179 --> 01:01:33,979
<font color="yellow">I said your place looked haunted,</font>

923
01:01:33,979 --> 01:01:35,619
<font color="yellow">and he got so upset at me.</font>

924
01:01:37,379 --> 01:01:40,279
<font color="yellow">At the time, I didn't get why he was so upset.</font>

925
01:01:40,579 --> 01:01:43,119
<font color="yellow">After I found out that you were his in-law,</font>

926
01:01:43,179 --> 01:01:45,219
<font color="yellow">I understood him clearly.</font>

927
01:01:46,949 --> 01:01:49,949
<font color="yellow">Because you are his in-law, I feel bad for you.</font>

928
01:01:50,619 --> 01:01:53,719
<font color="yellow">I am sorry about what I said to you that day.</font>

929
01:01:54,379 --> 01:01:55,519
<font color="yellow">You don't have to be.</font>

930
01:01:55,549 --> 01:01:57,349
<font color="yellow">So I prepared something for you.</font>

931
01:02:04,649 --> 01:02:06,179
<font color="yellow">What's this?</font>

932
01:02:06,449 --> 01:02:07,779
<font color="yellow">It's not a big amount,</font>

933
01:02:08,379 --> 01:02:10,779
<font color="yellow">but it will be enough for you...</font>

934
01:02:10,919 --> 01:02:12,919
<font color="yellow">to move out and get a place to live.</font>

935
01:02:15,019 --> 01:02:17,049
<font color="yellow">Do you understand what I am saying?</font>

936
01:02:18,249 --> 01:02:21,449
<font color="yellow">I want you to leave Director Han's house.</font>

937
01:02:42,719 --> 01:02:44,349
<font color="yellow">(Father, I'll Take Care of You)</font>

938
01:02:44,349 --> 01:02:45,649
<font color="yellow">Why are you doing this to me?</font>

939
01:02:46,219 --> 01:02:47,249
<font color="yellow">Do you like me?</font>

940
01:02:47,749 --> 01:02:50,149
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui, wake up.</font>

941
01:02:50,379 --> 01:02:52,319
<font color="yellow">Don't you think you're being too impudent?</font>

942
01:02:53,049 --> 01:02:55,319
<font color="yellow">Why would I go to the basement? It's too small anyway.</font>

943
01:02:55,579 --> 01:02:57,819
<font color="yellow">All right. Let's not see each other, then.</font>

944
01:02:58,019 --> 01:02:59,579
<font color="yellow">I won't see you ever again.</font>

945
01:02:59,949 --> 01:03:01,079
<font color="yellow">Are you laughing right now?</font>

946
01:03:01,419 --> 01:03:02,619
<font color="yellow">Should I cry, then?</font>

947
01:03:02,779 --> 01:03:04,719
<font color="yellow">Why are you so upset?</font>

948
01:03:04,979 --> 01:03:06,179
<font color="yellow">Cheer up.</font>

949
01:03:06,779 --> 01:03:08,819
<font color="yellow">Merry Christmas.</font>

